videos.description: Jordan Bone sends his defender sliding to the ground to get the easy layup.
videos.headline: Tennessee's Bone sends defender sliding

videos.description: Jared Harper misses the layup but Anfernee McLemore gets the offensive board and putback dunk.
videos.headline: McLemore throws down putback dunk for Auburn

videos.description: Bryce Brown lobs up the alley-oop to Horace Spencer who grabs it with one hand and throws down the dunk.
videos.headline: Tigers connect on massive alley-oop

videos.description: Chris Darrington completes the full-court pass up to Grant Williams who makes the fast-break dunk.
videos.headline: Tennessee scores on leak out dunk

videos.description: Mustapha Heron gets the steal on one end of the court then takes it up for the massive one-handed dunk.
videos.headline: Auburn's Heron throws down huge fast-break dunk

videos.description: Auburn opens up conference play with a win at Tennessee, extending their winning streak to 11 games.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCB Highlight (Auburn continues win streak with upset over Tennessee) 2018/01/02

videos.headline: Auburn continues win streak with upset over Tennessee
